    {{> header }} <!-- This assumes you have a header partial to include -->

    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h1 class="text-center mb-4">About Us</h1>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <p class="lead">Workout Tracker is dedicated to helping you reach your fitness goals. Our platform allows you to track your workouts, monitor progress, and stay motivated with a supportive community.</p>
                <p>Since our inception in 2023, we have been committed to providing an intuitive and comprehensive tool for fitness enthusiasts of all levels. Our easy-to-use interface means you can spend more time working out and less time managing your fitness plan.</p>
                <p>Our Team:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Jane Doe:</strong> A fitness enthusiast and software developer, Jane founded Workout Tracker to merge her passions for technology and health.</li>
                    <li><strong>John Smith:</strong> With a background in personal training, John brings expertise in exercise science to the platform, ensuring all our features support effective workout routines.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Thank you for choosing Workout Tracker as your fitness companion. We're excited to be part of your fitness journey!</p>
                <p>If you have any questions or feedback, please feel free to <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    {{> footer }} 

